USAir
Club
Do you want to enjoy a relaxing, private getaway
before, between or after flights —join the Club. The
USAir Club. We offer 29 USAir Clubs in 23 major
airport locations.
You will enjoy the advantages of one of the world's
finest airline clubs-including:
• Free use of photocopiers and personal
computers at every Club location
• Friendly, experienced USAir Club staff
Club locations for a nominal fee
• Facsimile machine use with a credit card
• Cocktail service, plus free soft drinks,
coffee, juice and snacks
To begin enjoying First Class treatment from the
ground up, complete the application at the back of
this timetable, or stop by any USAir ticket counter
or USAir Club location.
WITH OUR CONNECTIONS,
YOU CAN GO A LONG WAY.
•USAIR
A USAIR EXPRESS
•USAIR/USAIR EXPRESS
Together, USAir and USAir Express have over 5,000 flights a day to more
than 270 cities across the U.S. and Canada. Plus flights to Bermuda, the Bahamas,
Puerto Rico, London, Frankfurt and Paris. So when it's time to travel, remember the
airlines that are well connected: USAir and USAir Express. For reservations and
information, call your travel consultant or USAir toll-free 1(800)428-4322.
